on the social networks.

883
00:51:34,560 --> 00:51:36,280
The pink bunny phone.

884
00:51:36,480 --> 00:51:38,600
It's Manon Bechet's phone,
the florist.

885
00:51:39,800 --> 00:51:42,160
Doesn't it seem like a coincidence?

886
00:51:42,360 --> 00:51:45,280
Absolutely. So, first link:
the flowers.

887
00:51:45,480 --> 00:51:48,760
Because the flowers were bought
in Manon's shop.

888
00:51:48,920 --> 00:51:50,320
You know what?

889
00:51:50,520 --> 00:51:52,440
She's part of the cards club.

890
00:51:52,600 --> 00:51:54,760
I loved playing cards
when I was young.

891
00:51:55,200 --> 00:51:56,480
I'll leave you then.

892
00:51:56,600 --> 00:51:57,640
Goodbye, ma'am.

893
00:51:59,360 --> 00:52:02,160
-I'm going to clean up .
-No, this is a crime scene.

894
00:52:02,280 --> 00:52:03,480
Don't touch anything.

895
00:52:14,760 --> 00:52:15,600
Yes, Captain?

896
00:52:15,920 --> 00:52:18,160
Oscar, it's Marleau.
What did you find?

897
00:52:18,800 --> 00:52:21,880
At first glance, it looked like

898
00:52:22,080 --> 00:52:25,040
an erotic game gone bad

899
00:52:25,200 --> 00:52:28,080
